title: Chiefs, Saints, Browns, Tom Brady, and where Colin was right & wrong
itunes:title: Chiefs, Saints, Browns, Tom Brady, and where Colin was right & wrong
description:
Colin explains why he was more impressed with the Saints loss, than the Chiefs victory, the continuing saga of drama going on with the Browns, what might happened to Tom Brady at the end of this season, and where he was right and wrong over the weekend. Guests include Trent Dilfer, Tom Curran, Urban Meyer, and Tony Gonzalez.
